Nightreign The Forsaken Hollows Beginner Guide - MUST KNOW TIPS to Help You Win!
In this Elden Ring Nightreign video, I'm going to be talking about some useful information on how to clear the Forsaken Hollows Map a bit more effectively for those of you out there that are struggling either with the verticality of the map or you're just having a hard time because you don't have the path memorized like you do in the base game. I'm going to be giving you some tips of things that I have found useful so far.
